# Auth & Onboarding

## Phase machine

Owned by `AppState.phase` / `onboardingStep` (1…3). Do not replace with `NavigationStack` for the auth funnel unless redesigning the whole flow.

| Phase | View |
|---|---|
| `.welcome` | `WelcomeView` |
| `.email` | `EmailSignUpView` |
| `.onboarding` | `OnboardingFlow` → Year / Name / Interests |
| `.app` | `MainAppView` |

```swift
// Advance
withAnimation(.easeInOut(duration: 0.35)) { app.phase = .onboarding }
app.advanceOnboarding()   // steps 1→2→3 then finishOnboarding()

// Back from step 1 → welcome; else decrement onboardingStep
```

## Visual rules for this folder

- Full-bleed `GGColor.black` (or `GGBackground`), not gradient aurora (`AuroraBlobs` is a no-op).
- Headline brand uses `Wordmark`; taglines use `.explanatory` (New York).
- Questions posed by Madeleine: `MadeleineBubble` + `MiniOrb`; progress via `ProgressDots`.
- Primary continue actions: `AccentButton` or blue capsule patterns already in Welcome/Email.
- Cap bubble width (~320) so copy wraps; never let onboarding text overflow horizontally.
